          0.5,
          1
        ],
        "fixedToneGamma": 0.5
      },
      "comparisonTolerance": 1e-12,
      "rules": [
        "At every nonzero tone probe, the centered 0.5 control output equals raw tone within tolerance.",
        "Gamma outputs are strictly decreasing at controls 0, 0.5, 1 for every probe with raw tone strictly between 0 and 1.",
        "Contrast outputs are strictly decreasing for light probes with raw tone below 0.5 and strictly increasing for dark probes with raw tone above 0.5.",
        "At every zero-region probe, permission and effective mask-weighted tone remain exactly 0 for all nine gamma/contrast pairs from values 0, 0.5, 1.",
        "At the partial-alpha probe, permission equals expectedAlphaByte / 255 within tolerance and effective tone equals adjusted tone multiplied by permission."
      ],
